          p 
            img.img-star(src="/images/hand_draw_star.png")
            img.img-star(src="/images/hand_draw_star.png") 
            | Our mission is built on three core principles
            img.img-star(src="/images/hand_draw_star.png")
            img.img-star(src="/images/hand_draw_star.png") 
          ol#bullet-points
            li Fostering collaboration between the animation industry and AI technology
            li Inspiring creative innovation within the field, particularly for independent creators.
            li Creating a win-win scenario that benefits both the animation industry and technological advancement.
